{"ANTIVACCINATION":[{"def":"Opposition to vaccination.","pos":""}],"ANTIVACCINATIONIST":[{"def":"An antivaccinist.","pos":""}],"ANTIVACCINIST":[{"def":"One opposed to vaccination.","pos":""}],"ANTIVARIOLOUS":[{"def":"Preventing the contagion of smallpox.","pos":""}],"ANTIVENEREAL":[{"def":"Good against venereal poison; antisyphilitic.","pos":""}],"ANTIVENIN":[{"def":"The serum of blood rendered antitoxic to a venom by repeated injections of small doses of the venom.","pos":""}],"ANTIVIVISECTION":[{"def":"Opposition to vivisection.","pos":""}],"ANTIVIVISECTIONIST":[{"def":"An`ti*viv`i*sec\"tion*ist, n.","pos":""}]}